  "A plan that only covers hospital stays when viewed through a simplified analytical lens": "",
  "An HDHP has a higher deductible (at least $1,600 individual in 2024) and lower premiums. The key benefit is eligibility for HSA contributions, providing triple tax advantages.": "",
  "What does 'uninsured/underinsured motorist coverage' protect against?": "",
  "Mechanical breakdowns of your own vehicle": "",
  "Tickets and fines from traffic violations": "",
  "Damage to your car from natural disasters": "",
  "Injuries and damages caused by a driver who has no insurance or insufficient insurance to cover your losses": "",
