  "Sam earns $95,000 and is comparing disability insurance quotes. Policy A replaces 60% of income with a 30-day elimination period for $180/month. Policy B replaces 60% with a 90-day period for $110/month. If disabled, how much more does Sam pay out of pocket with Policy B during the extra 60-day wait?": "",
